summary: Sushankarapada Prasad is a second year student from the EC department at NIT, Jamshedpur.
Candidate has experience working on a career intake project for students, using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create dynamic pages.
The candidate has gained confidence in resolving conflicts while working on projects in GitHub.
The candidate is indicating that they will see the interviewer again in the future.
The candidate started with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, but upgraded to React and Tailwind CSS for improved performance and faster loading times on front pages.
